---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="about" description="the operator — personnel dossier">
  <div class="pane-grid">
    <div class="pane pane-profile stagger-in">
      <div class="pane-tab">profile</div>
      <div class="pane-content">
        <img src="/img/elma.webp" alt="seg6" class="about-avatar" />
        <div class="pane-fields">
          <div class="dossier-field">
            <span class="dossier-label">handle</span>
            <span class="dossier-value">seg6</span>
          </div>
          <div class="dossier-field">
            <span class="dossier-label">role</span>
            <span class="dossier-value">software engineer</span>
          </div>
          <div class="dossier-field">
            <span class="dossier-label">location</span>
            <span class="dossier-value">berlin, de</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pane pane-bio stagger-in" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
      <div class="pane-tab">readme</div>
      <div class="pane-content pane-prose">
        <p>
          I like knowing how things actually work. Not the polished abstraction, the thing underneath it. I've been programming ever since I was 14, and most of my career has basically been an excuse to keep following that impulse.
        </p>
        <p>
          One of the first times that really clicked for me was during an internship at an industrial automation company in İzmir, where I built an open-source SLMP library that ended up being used in production across factories in Turkey. After that, finishing my degree felt less important than continuing to build, so I dropped out and did exactly that.
        </p>
        <p>
          Since then I've worked on a bit of everything: systems code, backend services, cloud infrastructure, desktop apps, and product work. None of it was especially planned. I just kept following interesting problems, and eventually that brought me to Berlin.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not working, I'm usually reading about how minds, organisms, or physical systems work. I'm not especially disciplined about it, I just keep getting pulled into things I want to understand better, and find interesting.
        </p>
        <p>
          This blog is a place to write some of that down.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pane pane-bg stagger-in" style="animation-delay: 160ms">
      <div class="pane-tab">background</div>
      <div class="pane-content">
        <div class="dossier-field">
          <span class="dossier-label">education</span>
          <span class="dossier-value">bsc eee (dropped out), izmir bakırçay university</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dossier-field">
          <span class="dossier-label">stack</span>
          <span class="dossier-value">rust, c, go, c#, lua, python, typescript</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dossier-field">
          <span class="dossier-label">languages</span>
          <span class="dossier-value">english, turkish, german</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pane pane-links stagger-in" style="animation-delay: 240ms">
      <div class="pane-tab">find me</div>
      <div class="pane-content">
        <div class="dossier-field">
          <span class="dossier-label">github</span>
          <span class="dossier-value"><a href="https://github.com/seg6">gh/seg6</a></span>
        </div>
        <div class="dossier-field">
          <span class="dossier-label">email</span>
          <span class="dossier-value">hi@seg6.space</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dossier-field">
          <span class="dossier-label">linkedin</span>
          <span class="dossier-value"><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/omer-faruk">/in/omer-faruk</a></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pane pane-exp stagger-in" style="animation-delay: 320ms">
      <div class="pane-tab">experience</div>
      <div class="pane-content pane-content-flush">
        <div class="exp-row">
          <span class="exp-org">meyer sound</span>
          <span class="exp-dates">jan 2025 – present</span>
          <span class="exp-role">software engineer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-row">
          <span class="exp-org">deta</span>
          <span class="exp-dates">jul 2023 – jan 2025</span>
          <span class="exp-role">software engineer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-row">
          <span class="exp-org">sartura</span>
          <span class="exp-dates">apr 2023 – dec 2023</span>
          <span class="exp-role">software engineer (contract)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-row">
          <span class="exp-org">geotek</span>
          <span class="exp-dates">apr 2023 – jul 2023</span>
          <span class="exp-role">software engineer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-row">
          <span class="exp-org">geotek</span>
          <span class="exp-dates">jul 2022 – sep 2022</span>
          <span class="exp-role">intern</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
